fields.name: name
docs: The name of the asset

docs: The symbol for the asset

docs: URI pointing to JSON representing the asset

fields.name: seller_fee_basis_points
docs: Royalty basis points that goes to creators in secondary sales (0-10000)

fields.name: collection
docs: Collection

types.name: Auction
docs: Created by the Token owner, holds the most updated data of the Auction

fields.name: end_time
docs: Timestamp until which the `Auction` accepts bids

fields.name: seller
docs: Owner of the cNFT and creator of the `Auction`

fields.name: rent_payer
docs: The signing account that originally paid rent for the Auction and ATAs creation.
And to which the rent is returned upon Auction finalization

fields.name: payment_currency
docs: The mint in which this individual `Auction` is based

types.name: AuctionTimeExtension
docs: Data related to how the Auctions should be extended if they receive a bid
when they are about to close

fields.name: time_threshold
docs: Minimum amount of seconds remaining in auction to extend its duration

fields.name: additional_secs
docs: Seconds added to previous finalization if auction is under [`time_threshold`]

types.name: Config
docs: Holds all the general configuration for the program

fields.name: treasury_mint
docs: Mint for the [`fees_treasury`]

fields.name: share
docs: The percentage share.
The value is a percentage, not basis points.
